      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes some of the QoS-based routing issues and requirements, and proposes a framework for QoS-based routing in the Internet.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
